tps://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnebybo%2Fstatus%2F1197898799663894529&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=cf9b3fca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnebybo%2Fstatus%2F1197898799663894529&h=ab630d62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Anebybo/status/1197898799663894529</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Christoffer Karlsson (Sweden)<br />\n@mysliberal<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mysliberal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmysliberal&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=7e743467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mysliberal</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Andrew Khoo (Malaysia)<br />\n<br />\nMs. Miriam Lexmann (Slovakia)<br />\n<br />\nMs. Simona Mohamsson (Sweden)<br />\n@SMohamsson<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SMohamsson\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSMohamsson&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=091e73d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SMohamsson</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Michael Palicz (US)<br />\n@Mike_Palicz<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Mike_Palicz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMike_Palicz&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=6c8d243c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Mike_Palicz</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Luke de Pulford (United Kingdom)  <br />\n@lukedepulford<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1198399042444652545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1198399042444652545&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=cbe42014\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1198399042444652545&h=dd130ac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1198399042444652545</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Thomas Rohden (Denmark)<br />\n@ThomasRohden<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThomasRohden/status/1198409247740047361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThomasRohden%2Fstatus%2F1198409247740047361&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=2a16c731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThomasRohden%2Fstatus%2F1198409247740047361&h=6f53f154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ThomasRohden/status/1198409247740047361</a><br />\n<br />\nMs. Emmy Scilaris (Sweden)<br />\n<br />\n特別嘉賓:<br />\n所羅門 NCM Yue @SolomonYue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=0d742e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a>"},{"pid":"21701918718d056204f3ac7d51a827fa958fcd1f","tid":1749295,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"傳真社致全體手足：全民監察選票！每小時投票人數寫在票站出面！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1747423/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1747423/page/1</a><br />\n由於今年有隨時關閉票站的風險，如大家當日可以幫忙，請預先加入telegram群組 <a href=\"http://t.me/factwire_DCelection2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffactwire_DCelection2019&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=f9345f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/factwire_DCelection2019</a> ，以方便協調，多謝各位。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/factwire/posts/1269448973262154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fposts%2F1269448973262154&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=e32747ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/factwire/posts/1269448973262154</a><br />\n<br />\n【任務】齊齊做《鏗鏘集》的新聞線眼！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1747566/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1747566/page/1</a><br />\n若留意到任何異常或可疑情況、無分政治立場或黨派，都懇請你們在安全情況下，拍攝片段或相片透過 whatsapp（91829284）向《鏗鏘集》報料（註：票站內不可拍攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthk.HKConnection/posts/2535920163123717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthk.HKConnection%2Fposts%2F2535920163123717&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=a150db26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthk.HKConnection/posts/2535920163123717</a><br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處 2891 1001<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/contact/contact.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fcontact%2Fcontact.htm&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=d9e2be99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/contact/contact.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有漏唔該加上去<br />\n同埋缺外媒list, 有冇人加上去<br />\n幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"e17da9ebd2e0c05379c3f6d4ddb90dbaa8d53184","tid":1749295,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"自推10連 1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35eff3a64f97e45612855cee72286a7e3226be1","tid":1749295,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f6636b82992d57afe4d8abcdc2bafcce07d245","tid":1749295,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5048d0f1cb9dd56f0a06bea84a68ab3f961f93","tid":1749295,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f83e24ee0ad6e6d0287c5540227f76f7b63bd7e","tid":1749295,"uid":1